Class Description
App
The runnable application class used to initialization the Main Screen class and launch the GUI.
BarGraphViewController
Graph View Controller controls displays 7 different bar graphs based on user input from Graph Menu Controller.
CompareController
The controller, used by / linked to, the compares FXML file.
Comparer
This class adds a set of static methods that allow reports to distance and time to be compared.
ComparerTest
Testing that the comparer class correctly is able to compare two reports and return valid result.
ControllerData
This class acts as a connection between the controllers passing data through here so that only the controller's initialization it can get the relevant data it needs.
ControllerDataTest  
Crime
Used to create and store crime objects.
CrimeFrequency
A class that holds a String date and int frequency, a list of crime frequency is used for crime over graphing
CrimeTest

CustomException
A custom exception that allows for the type of exception to be stored as a string in the info field.

This class works to link the SQLite database with our java application.

Tests the features of importing and getting data using the data accessor.

FilterConditions
a class used to encapsulate the fields that data can be filtered by.

Controller class.
GeneralMenuController

GraphMenuController
Graph Menu Controller is the class which controls which graph is displayed by the program.
GraphUtil
A set of static utility methods that prepares material for the graph view classes, such as ranking data based on frequency or preparing strings to be displayed as a graph title.
GraphUtilTest
Tests ranking reports.
InputType
The types of input validators that can be applied to a Node.
InputValidator
Used to prepare and validate input nodes.
LineGraphViewController

MapController

MenuController
The controller, used by / linked to, the Menu FXML file.
PageController
This class creates the paginator that then itself generates the tables, that are used to store selections of the database's information.
PSTypes
This class adds a set of static methods that are used when checking if a CSV is null which is "" inserting the corrected null value into the database.
PSTypeTest
Tests to ensure that data inserted using the PSType classes methods are correctly inserted into the database.
QueryBuilder
Builds queries based on parameters and returns them as Strings
QueryBuilderTest
Tests to ensure that where query is correctly generated when called.
Report
Used to create and store report objects which is the super class of Crime.
SearchMenuController
This menu allows a user to pick a field to search and then attempts to match text entered by the user to that in the database.
Serializer
A class used to serialize objects and store them in a file, and to deserialize them back into objects
StartScreenController
The controller, used by / linked to, the Start Screen FXML file.
Tuple<X,​Y>
Tuple class used for converting hash table into sorted list for the "GraphUtil" data class.
